      section#judges
        h2 Judges
        p(style='') Yet to be announced.
      section#sponsors
        h2 Sponsors
        p(style='') If you wish to sponsor our event for developer, entrepreneur and investor outreach and to encourage student hackers, please contact us at team@osid.in 
        | We thank our awesome sponsors for all their help. The sponsor listing will be out soon.
      section#rules
        h2 Rules for participation
          h5 Registration
          p To participate, fill in the registration form given above. Last date for registration is 20th October, 2012.

          h5 Eligibility
          p You should a student to participate in the event. No constraints on your course, stream or year.

          h5 Screening
          p The screening will be based on your best hack as mentioned in the registration form. 

          h5 Theme
          p The theme will be declared two days before the event.

          h5 Team size
          p Based on the screening the team size will be decided. Tentatively, the maximum team size will be 3. The teams will be made on the day of the hackathon.

          h5 Duration
          p This is a 24 hour hackday, starting 10:00 AM on Saturday, November 3rd.

          h5 Presentation
          p At the end of the hackday, each team has to present their hack to our judges in 10 minutes. You are required to prepare a short presentation and demo your hack. Only the work done during the hackathon can be presented. Any team presenting pre-existing work will be disqualified. Mention clearly what your hack is and if you have used pre-existing work.
